f `drain()` | 80 |\n| 8 | MINOR | `LanDiscoveryConfig` missing `max_peers > 0` validation | 75 |\n\nThe most important findings are issues 1 and 2. Issue 1 (SEC-2) is a concrete code change that contradicts an explicit plan requirement. Issue 2 (SEC-3) is a known deferred chunk but needs a prominent `FIXME` at the call site or it will be forgotten. Issue 6 is a correctness risk given Tokio's silent task-panic behavior. Issues 3 and 4 are latent rather than immediate, but both will surface as subtle bugs as the controller grows.</result>\n<usage><total_tokens>34889</total_tokens><tool_uses>26</tool_uses><duration_ms>121337</duration_ms></usage>\n</task-notification>\nFull transcript available at: /tmp/claude-1000/-home-leon0399-Projects-reme/36b495c0-95b9-49fc-8523-b911e74011a9/tasks/a5c2eac4983dc3860.output",
